         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 2636, recto: (1) Pa-- has paid (2) Psemmonthes, son of Pasemis, son of Meswer, has paid (3) to Pamonthes, son of Psenamounis, and Pamonthes, son of Psenanoubis, (4) for the dues of the bath (5) in year 32, 1 kite. Written in year 32, Mesore 22.</ab>
